46. Eur Heart J. 2020 Mar 14;41(11):1190-1199. doi: 10.1093/eurheartj/ehz239.

Prediction of individualized lifetime benefit from cholesterol lowering, blood 
pressure lowering, antithrombotic therapy, and smoking cessation in apparently 
healthy people.

Jaspers NEM(1), Blaha MJ(2), Matsushita K(3), van der Schouw YT(4), Wareham 
NJ(5), Khaw KT(6), Geisel MH(7), Lehmann N(7), Erbel R(7), Jöckel KH(7), van der 
Graaf Y(4), Verschuren WMM(4)(8), Boer JMA(8), Nambi V(9)(10), Visseren FLJ(1), 
