Inc. All rights reserved.

DOI: 10.1016/j.chest.2019.04.109
PMID: 31103695 [Indexed for MEDLINE]


50. Value Health Reg Issues. 2019 Dec;20:86-94. doi: 10.1016/j.vhri.2019.03.002. 
